sourceMeaningMnemonic: The <radical>commander</radical> radical and the <kanji>commander</kanji> kanji are the same!
readingMnemonic: Who is the <kanji>commander</kanji> of Japan? The <reading>Shou</reading>gun (<ja>しょう</ja>)! And if you ever say anyone else or vote for someone else or even THINK about someone else being the commander, he'll find you and cut off your head.
readingInfo: You better remember the Shougun is the commander of everything... or else...
